                            <td>
                                Holidays and festivals are among some of the
                                most exciting things about the Indian
                                experience. They are vibrant expressions of the
                                depth and diversity of Indian culture. In the
                                Hindu calendar, there is a holiday for almost
                                every day of the year, although many of them
                                are not widely celebrated. Knowing about the
                                various festivals in and around Bangalore can
                                enrich your cultural experience and also help
                                you avoid severe traffic jams from time to
                                time.
                            </td>
