                                <br/>
                                <em>North India and Tamil Nadu</em>
                                <p align="justify">
                                    <strong>Pooram</strong>
                                    <br/>
                                    In Trichur, Kerala, this temple festival is
                                    celebrated with grandeur. Elephants wear
                                    spectacular decorations for the day-long
                                    musical procession. The festival ends with
                                    a magnificent fireworks display.
                                    <br/>
                                    <em>Kerala</em>
