                                <br/>
                                <strong>Rath Yatra </strong>
                                <br/>
                                <img
                                    src="http://www.owcbangalore.org/images/rathyatra.jpg"
                                    width="120"
                                    height="120"
                                    align="right"
                                />
                                Rath Yatra marks the journey Krishna took from
                                his home to Mathura to kill his evil uncle. His
                                images, along with those of his brother and
                                sister, are paraded in the streets of Puri,
                                Orissa, on huge chariots that require 4,000
                                people to pull them!
                                <br/>
